87 0 obj
  << /ActualText (As the final step in our research\054 we developed schematic frameworks to systematically organize the major similarities and differences among the selected species\056 \n\nThis approach enabled us to identify their predominant emotions\054 trace how these have evolved over time\054 and analyze their interplay with environmental factors\056 \n\nWe concluded that each species exhibits a characteristic dominant emotion\024for instance\054 bees demonstrate sociability\054 while elephants are distinguished by empathy\056)
     /K [ 1 ]
     /P 90 0 R
